==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spectral
<hw>Spec"tral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of or
pertaining to a specter; ghosty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He that feels timid at the <qex>spectral</qex> form of evil is not
the man to spread light.</q> <rj><qau>F. W. Robertson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Opt.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the spectrum;
made by the spectrum; <as>as, <ex>spectral</ex> colors;
<ex>spectral</ex> analysis.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Spectral lemur</b></col>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <cd>See
<er>Tarsius</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spectrally</ent>⟦br⟧
